<h3 id="avoiding-auto-moderation">Avoiding auto moderation</h3>

<p>That has very little to do with what Iâ€™m writing about today but it sets a good stage. Creators walk on egg shells to avoid upsetting the algorithm â€“ they donâ€™t want to send any wrong signals. From a Human-Computer Interaction point of view this is amazing but, again, not directly related to the following.</p>

